<translation id="6433172051771630690">Amathiphu okuthola okuningi ku-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="6502321914804101924">I-Cobalt Iphume Ngemvume</translation>
<translation id="6563921047760808519">Funda kabanzi mayelana <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />nokuthi i-Cobalt igcina kanjani idatha yakho iyimfihlo<ph name="END_LINK" /></translation>
<translation id="6625409903340039086">I-Cobalt manje isekela izinqubomgomo zomsebenzisi ku-akhawunti yakho ephethwe</translation>
