<translation id="6752854822223394465">Inhlangano yakho isetha i-Cobalt...</translation>
<translation id="6794054469102824109">Ivula iGeyimu ye-Dino ye-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="6820823224820483452">I-Cobalt ayikwazanga ukuhlola wonke amaphasiwedi. Zama futhi kusasa.</translation>
<translation id="6830362027989570433">Ukubuka Okunwetshiwe Kokugcwalisa Okuzenzakalelayo kwe-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="6852799557929001644">Finyelela amaphasiwedi akho e-Cobalt nokuningi kuwo wonke amanye ama-app kule divayisi.</translation>
<translation id="6887138405044152640">Ukuze uthumele le thebhu kwenye idivayisi, ngena ngemvume ku-Cobalt lapho.</translation>
<translation id="6911341667534646387">Qhubeka usebenzisa idatha ye-Cobalt ku-Google Account yakho</translation>
<translation id="7006920032187763988">Ungasebenzisa amaphasiwedi owalondolozile ku-Password Manager kwamanye ama-app ku-iPad yakho.</translation>
<translation id="7018284295775193585">I-Cobalt ayikwazi ukubuyekeza</translation>
<translation id="7045244423563602563">Yenza i-Cobalt Ibe Ngeyakho</translation>
<translation id="7055269218854630176">Inhlangano yakho, <ph name="DOMAIN" /> iphatha i-akhawunti ongena kuyo ngemvume kanye nendlela engasetshenziswa ngayo i-Cobalt. Umlawuli wakho angasetha noma abeke umkhawulo ezakhini ezithile.</translation>
<translation id="7099326575020694068">I-Cobalt ayikwazi ukusebenzisa ikhamera yakho kumodi yokubuka okuhlukanisiwe</translation>
<translation id="7163483974919055112">Sesha Okubukwayo ku-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="7165402419892018581">Khetha i-Cobalt Yokugcwalisa Okuzenzakalelayo</translation>
<translation id="7175400662502680481">Iphasiwedi yakho idalulwe ekwephulweni kwesivumelwano sedatha. I-Password Manager incoma ukuba uyishintshe manje.</translation>
<translation id="7192111075364461693">Izaziso ze-Cobalt zivaliwe kumasethingi edivayisi yakho.</translation>
<translation id="7198580735512160509">Ukuze uziqokele okuphakelwa yi-Discover ne-Cobalt, vula ukuvumelanisa.</translation>
<translation id="7222001353246886083">Sesha okuthi ${searchPhrase} ku-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="725427773388857052">I-Cobalt ingakusiza ukukugcina uphephile ekuphulweni kwesivumelwano sedatha, kumawebhusayithi angaphephile nokuningi.</translation>
<translation id="7269362888766543920">Ezinye izengezo zibangela i-Cobalt ukuthi iphahlazeke. Sicela uzikhiphe.</translation>
<translation id="7285031092584344905">Finyelela amaphasiwedi akho e-Cobalt nokunye okwengeziwe kuwo wonke amanye ama-app.</translation>
<translation id="7313655110045230863">Ukuze wenze i-Cobalt ibe yisiphequluli sakho esizenzakalelayo, vula Amasethingi. Thepha Uhlelo lokusebenza Lwesiphequluli Esizenzakalelayo, bese ukhetha i-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="7337881442233988129">Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="7357211569052832586">Idatha ekhethiwe isusiwe kusukela ku-Cobalt nakumadivayisi avumelanisiwe. I-akhawunti yakho ye-Google kungenzeka ibe nezinye izindlela zokuphequlula ezifana nosesho nomsebenzi kusukela kwamanye amasevisi e-Google ku-history.google.com.</translation>
<translation id="7387082980875012885">Vula Ithebhu Entsha Ku-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="7395825497086981028">Iphasiwedi yakho izolondolozwa ku-Password Manager ye-<ph name="EMAIL" />.</translation>
<translation id="7400689562045506105">Sebenzisa i-Cobalt yonke indawo</translation>
<translation id="7523464085759699266">Vula “Ukhiya Wamathebhu e-Incognito Uma Uvala i-Cobalt.”</translation>
<translation id="7601597633134889942">Vakashela isayithi bese uchofoza okuthi Landela kumenyu ye-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="7674213385180944843">Vula izilungiselelo &gt; Ubumfihlo &gt; Ikhamera &gt; i-Cobalt uphinde uvule ikhamera.</translation>
<translation id="7710137812207066069">Vula Ithebhu Entsha Ku-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="7747820849741499258">Sesha ku-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="7763454117143368771">Sebenzisa i-Cobalt njengesiphequluli sakho esiyinhloko ukuze uhlale uvikelekile kumasayithi ayingozi futhi ugcine amphasiwedi akho aphephile</translation>
<translation id="78025249032851484">I-Cobalt yakho isiphelelwe yisikhathi.</translation>
<translation id="7859018312476869945">Uma uthayipha ibha yekheli noma ibhokisi losesho, i-Cobalt ithumela lokho okuthayiphayo kunjini yakho yosesho yokuzenzakalelayo ukuze uthole iziphakamiso ezingcono. Lokhu kuvaliwe ku-Incognito.</translation>
<translation id="786327964234957808">Ushintsha ama-akhawunti okuvumelanisa kusukela ku-<ph name="USER_EMAIL1" /> ukuya ku-<ph name="USER_EMAIL1" />. Idatha yakho ekhona ye-Cobalt iphethwe yi-<ph name="DOMAIN" />. Lokhu kuzosusa idatha kusukela kule divayisi, kodwa idatha yakho izohlala ku-<ph name="USER_EMAIL2" />.</translation>
<translation id="7865408467687426957">Uma ungene ngemvume ku-Cobalt, amaphasiwedi owalondolozayo azongena ku-Google Account yakho. Ukuze uvale lokhu, <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />iya kumasethingi<ph name="END_LINK" />.</translation>
<translation id="7890287942691234100">Qala ukusebenzisa iskena se-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="7905064834449738336">Uma usebenzisa iphasiwedi, i-Cobalt iyakuxwayisa uma ishicilelwe ku-inthanethi. Uma yenza lokhu, amaphasiwedi akho namagama abasebenzisi ayabethelwa, ukuze angakwazi ukufundwa yinoma ngubani, kubandakanya ne-Google.</translation>
