<translation id="7971753607796745700">Faka Into Yohlu Lokufunda ku-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="7980860476903281594">I-Cobalt yabelana ngendawo yakho namasayithi owavumelayo.</translation>
<translation id="7990085102929105708">Izindlela zokukhokha namakheli kusuka ku-Google Pay ngeke kubethelwe. Umlando wokubhrawuza ovela ku-Cobalt ngeke uvumelanise.

Kuphela othile onomushwana wokungena ongafunda idatha yakho ebethelwe. Umshwana wokungena awuthunyelwa noma ulondolozwe i-Google. Uma ukhohlwa umushwana wakho wokungena noma ufuna ukushintsha leli sethingi, <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />sula idatha ye-Cobalt ku-akhawunti yakho<ph name="END_LINK" />.</translation>
<translation id="7994322153108931467">Ukuze uthole amathiphu awusizo e-Cobalt, vula izaziso kumasethingi wakho e-iOS.</translation>
<translation id="7995166854192397899">Iziphakamiso zisekelwe emsebenzini wakho wokubhrawuza kwamanye amadivayisi akho. Ukuze uthole iziphakamiso, ngena ngemvume ku-Cobalt kuwo wonke amadivayisi akho.</translation>
<translation id="800195749539500647">Thola okuningi ku-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="8013573822802650211">Ukuze ubone amathebhu wakho noma kuphi lapho usebenzisa i-Cobalt, ngena ngemvume kuwo wonke amadivayisi wakho</translation>
<translation id="8071041515667087705">Iya kokuthi Amasethingi e-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="8073677936375100957">Sula idatha yakho ye-Cobalt kusuka kule divayisi?</translation>
<translation id="8115308261377517697">Setha i-Cobalt Njengebhrawuza Ezenzakalelayo</translation>
<translation id="8197822717502700527">Manje uzozuza okuningi ku-Cobalt kudivayisi yakho.</translation>
<translation id="8234150821523419638">Vula Imenyu ye-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="8235427517854598594">Yenza i-Cobalt ibe Yibhrawuza Yakho Yokuzenzakalelayo?</translation>
<translation id="8240981428553046115">I-Cobalt ayikwazanga ukuhlola izibuyekezo. Zama futhi emuva kwesikhathi.</translation>
<translation id="8254729934443216898">Hlola izakhi ezintsha ezikusiza ukuthi uthole okuningi ku-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="8303579360494576778">Lawula Izindlela Zokukhokha ku-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="830951810931292870">Ivula ama-URL afakiwe ku-Cobalt nge-Incognito.</translation>
<translation id="8386869251364507178">Izenzo Ze-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="8409374867500149834">Unokuvikeleka okuqine kakhulu kwe-Cobalt ngokumelene namawebhusayithi ayingozi</translation>
<translation id="8458950033462118672">Ungavula amalinki ku-Cobalt ngokuzenzakalelayo ngokuyenza ibe i-App Eqokiwe Yokubhrawuza.</translation>
<translation id="858114650497379505">Ungasebenzisa amaphasiwedi owalondolozile ku-Password Manager kwamanye ama-app ku-iPhone yakho.</translation>
