Ukuze ushintshe la masethingi, <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />sula idatha ye-Cobalt ku-akhawunti yakho<ph name="END_LINK" />.</translation>
<translation id="865600487977764604">Kukugcina uphephile ku-Cobalt futhi kungase kusetshenziswe ukuthuthukisa ukuvikeleka kwakho kwamanye ama-app we-Google lapho ungene ngemvume.</translation>
<translation id="8663480472502753423">Gcina i-Cobalt isesikhathini</translation>
<translation id="8685813584220679697">Ngena ngemvume kuleli sayithi naku-Cobalt.</translation>
