<translation id="8747378496147986285">Uma ivuliwe:
<ph name="BEGIN_INDENT" />  • Siza ukwenza i-Cobalt ibe ngcono kubantu abayisebenzisa ngendlela owenza ngayo.<ph name="END_INDENT" />

Izinto okufanele uzicabangele:
<ph name="BEGIN_INDENT" />  • Ulwazi luthunyelwa ku-Google mayelana nokusebenzisa kwakho i-Cobalt, kodwa ayiboshelwanga kuwe.

  • Uma i-Cobalt iphahlazeka, imininingwane mayelana nokuphahlazeka ingase ihlanganise ulwazi oluthile lomuntu siqu.
  • Uma uvula ukuvumelanisa, ama-metric angase futhi afake ulwazi olumayelana nama-URL owavakashelayo.<ph name="END_INDENT" /></translation>
<translation id="8759037115129007407">Ilungu lakho lomndeni alikwazi ukwamukela amaphasiwedi khona manje. Licele libuyekeze i-Cobalt futhi livumelanise amaphasiwedi alo. <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />Funda kabanzi<ph name="END_LINK" /></translation>
<translation id="8776843108004031667">Le akhawunti kanye nanoma iyiphi idatha engalondolozwanga izosuswa ku-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="88376265765385899">Ivula amabhukhimakhi e-Cobalt.</translation>
<translation id="8860548555286245440">Vula ama-URL ku-Cobalt nge-Incognito</translation>
<translation id="8866191443434488382">I-Cobalt izobona izinombolo zokulandelela kumasayithi owavakashelayo futhi ikubonise izibuyekezo zephakheji ekhasini Lethebhu Entsha. Inombolo yolulandelela iphakheji negama lewebhusayithi kuzothunyelwa ku-Cobalt ukuze kunikezwe lesi sakhi futhi kuthuthukiswe izakhi zokuthenga zawo wonke umuntu. Ungabuyekeza lokhu noma nini kokuthi <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />Amasethingi Okulandelela Iphakheji<ph name="END_LINK" />.</translation>
<translation id="8909995017390087892">I-Cobalt ye-iOS</translation>
<translation id="8924617840944134898">Vula ithebhu ye-Cobalt ye-incognito</translation>
<translation id="894437814105052438">Lapho uphuma ngemvume, i-Cobalt ngeke ivumelanise noma iyiphi idatha entsha ku-akhawunti yakho ye-Google. Idatha evumelaniswe ngaphambilini ihlala kwi-akhawunti.</translation>
<translation id="8950326149985259075">{THRESHOLD,plural, =1{Lokhu kwenzeka lapho i-Cobalt ingasetshenziswa umzuzu ongu-{THRESHOLD}}one{Lokhu kwenzeka lapho i-Cobalt ingasetshenziswa imizuzu engu-{THRESHOLD}}other{Lokhu kwenzeka lapho i-Cobalt ingasetshenziswa imizuzu engu-{THRESHOLD}}}</translation>
<translation id="8963279154877372067">Vumela izaziso ze-Cobalt ukuthola izexwayiso zokwehla kwentengo</translation>
<translation id="900560297598578021">Ungene ngemvume njengo-<ph name="EMAIL" />.

Idatha yakho ibethelwe ngomushwana wakho wokungena ngo-<ph name="TIME" />. Ifake ukuze usebenzise futhi wonge idatha ye-Cobalt ku-Google Account yakho.</translation>
<translation id="9022552996538154597">Ngena ngemvume ku-Cobalt</translation>
<translation id="9050790730841755540">Sebenzisa i-Cobalt noma nini uma uthepha amalinki kwamanye ama-app.</translation>
<translation id="9059693977935746710">Ngeke kudingeke ukuthi ukhumbule le phasiwedi. Izolondolozwa Kusiphathi Sephasiwedi se-<ph name="EMAIL" /></translation>
<translation id="9089354809943900324">I-Cobalt ayikho kudethi</translation>
