<translation id="921174536258924340">I-Cobalt ayikwazanga ukuhlola wonke amaphasiwedi. Zama futhi kusasa noma <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />hlola amaphasiwedi ku-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google<ph name="END_LINK" /></translation>
